substep.ask:
Current name: {{command_name}}
Is this the right name? If not, what should it be?
Good names: /commit, /pr-review, /check-deps Avoid: /do-the-thing, /x, /commit_changes

substep.template-output:
Write the identity into the instructions.md frontmatter (NOT
command-config.yaml — that is just the vera build descriptor):

```yaml
---
description: {{description}}
{{#if argument_hint}}argument-hint: "{{argument_hint}}"{{/if}}
{{#if agent}}agent: {{agent}}{{/if}}
---
```

[a] Refine identity [c] Continue [y] YOLO
